{"tid":2117458,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"事隔一年,721事件的平行時空(多圖)","createTime":"2020-07-21T01:00:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T01:00:41.000Z","uid":59844,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"600eaf00fca6ba9fbaa7f52cc15fc08a87142fa9","tid":2117458,"uid":59844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T01:00:41.000Z","msg":"1.話說721事件前的當天日更時份已有白衣人手持鐵通在街道上流連<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q0uOWfX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq0uOWfX.jpg&h=2e8c9d65&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n2.到了晚上,白衣人開始在街上襲擊途人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TdRmwQE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTdRmwQE.jpg&h=fe925867&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AZDTnXm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAZDTnXm.jpg&h=0c95b3e6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n3.白衣人一直由街上追打途人到鐵路站,手持鐵通木棍藤條衝入車站向市民作無差別襲擊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uOnEiv7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuOnEiv7.jpg&h=e6b0e854&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/keWNspv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkeWNspv.jpg&h=ceb88d62&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7AKjiwb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7AKjiwb.jpg&h=23cae9a0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n4.不用39秒,警察迅速到場,並開槍將白衣人擊斃<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oKW5Ywr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoKW5Ywr.jpg&h=fbdb60a1&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SxXEiwt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSxXEiwt.jpg&h=e26172e4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n同樣是7月21日,同樣是白衣人無差別襲擊事件,遊戲中的NPC警察已迅速到場將白衣人制伏。<br />\n可怕的是我地現實中生活入面,當日警察用左39分鐘先到場,仲要同D白衣人拍晒膊頭,很可惜這就是當今的香港。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n721是我們不能忘記的歷史。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bgK7srX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbgK7srX.jpg&h=4ec55380&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同場加映:<br />\n火魔法火燒狗車,錘打閘大大(帶番個頭盔先,GTA V遊戲截圖限定,現實生活咁做會犯法,切勿模仿)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sf6Q9Go.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSf6Q9Go.jpg&h=c538bb36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FL2wT74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFL2wT74.jpg&h=1fd1198a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Fkyn1r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Fkyn1r.jpg&h=c6d0a878&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YtpOWms.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYtpOWms.jpg&h=136f977b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bWB5YzO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbWB5YzO.jpg&h=19a034cc&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}